lead by these two beams of light the “I Support Black Women” campaign to serves as an example of how fashion & the arts can better represent the under represented continues. Trinice McNally @ayo_zuri and Jamie Swift @blackwomenradicals lead a 2 hour discussion with @tara_mkc @svetchassol @rosende0702 bridging sentiments from across the globe. streaming now on @off___white___imaginary___tv 

the @off____white™ c/o @converse raffle is running now thru July 30th.

find out more and donate via https://canary---yellow.com @canary____yellow 

official terms available https://canary---yellow.com/

—

The “I Support Black Women” campaign aims to amplify and capture Black Women leaders of all identities (Transgender, Immigrant, Disabled, Fat, Queer, Working-Class) to share their work and why they have dedicated their life to social change. The campaign also supports a fundraiser to open a physical location for the @schoolforblackfeministpolitics (SBFP), a Black feminist political education initiative and hub.

i’m raffling 10 signed pairs of Off-White™ c/o Converse sneakers as and extension of the @off____white™ “I Support Black Women” campaign with @ayo_zuri & @jaimeeswift to fulfill our target to build a school.

limited to 10 pairs, raffle open now until July 30. 

All in support of @blackwomenradicals and “I Support Black Women” campaign ~ @post_____modern 

find out more and donate via link in bio https://canary---yellow.com @canary____yellow 

official terms available https://canary---yellow.com/

—

The “I Support Black Women” campaign aims to amplify and capture Black Women leaders of all identities (Transgender, Immigrant, Disabled, Fat, Queer, Working-Class) to share their work and why they have dedicated their life to social change. The campaign also supports a fundraiser to open a physical location for the @schoolforblackfeministpolitics (SBFP), a Black feminist political education initiative and hub.
